ios.subtitle: Don't Tap The White Tile Games

editorialNotes.standard: This rhythm-based platfomer is the kind of game that nestles in your head and won’t let go. Bouncing to a beat, you spring across gaps, between columns and over spikes—struggling to finish each wildly difficult stage. Slick controls make the game easy to pick up and play, but mastering its many challenges won’t come easily.
